    <h2>🕵️ Adversaries & Attacks</h2>

    <p>🔐 <b>WordPress Malware Masquerades as Plugin</b><br>
    WP-antymalwary-bot.php backdoor plugin allows RCE, ad injection, and admin logins via hardcoded password.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/news/wordpress-malware-masquerades/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>📥 <b>LockBit Delivered Automatically via Phorpiex Botnet</b><br>
    Phishing emails spread LockBit directly without manual intrusion, showing automation in ransomware delivery.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/news/phorpiex-botnet-delivers-lockbit/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🧛 <b>Gremlin Stealer Targets Credentials, Crypto, and Browsers</b><br>
    New infostealer exfiltrates sensitive data from browsers, wallets, Steam, and Discord to Telegram-controlled servers.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/news/new-gremlin-infostealer/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🌍 <b>Uyghur Community Targeted by Trojanized Text Editor</b><br>
    Citizen Lab found UyghurEditPP used to spy on Uyghur diaspora. Attackers inserted surveillance malware in the app.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.theregister.com/2025/04/29/citizen_lab_uyghur_phishing_malware/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
